text: Nanpei Memorial High School, also known as Kitti High School,"Higher Education in the Federated States of Micronesia ." Embassy of the Federated States of Micronesia Washington DC. Retrieved on February 23, 2018. "Kitti High School Wone Pohnpei State FM 96941" is a senior high school in Kitti, Pohnpei Island, Pohnpei State, Federated States of Micronesia. , the school, operated by the Pohnpei State Department of Education, has about 600 students."Secondary Division." Pohnpei State Department of Education.
